Expected functionality of this software:
* Register a new user
  * With Email confirmation
* Reset your password
  * Give your JID.
  * With Email confirmation
  * Form to set new password.
* Set email address of existing XMPP user.
  * Give your JID, password, new email.
  * With Email confirmation.
* Remove user
  * Give your JID and password.

Anti-Spam functionality:
* ReCAPTCHA
* hidden form field (filling out leads to immediate block!)
* limit to forms per second per IP
* submit form to fast leads to block
* add date-field, purpose and security hash, like in comments app.
